name: Unidentified_Pyke_(Ord_Mantell)
content:
A Pyke operated under the Pyke Syndicate during the early days of the Imperial Era. Around 19 BBY, the Pyke Syndicate made deals with the Durand crime family. After Roland Durand lost his spice to Cid and Clone Force 99, this Pyke held him hostage in Cid's Parlor on Ord Mantell. After meeting Clone Force 99, the Pyke made a deal where he kept the kid while the rest of the force obtained the missing spice. Once the spice was delivered, the Pyke then cut off one of Roland Durand's horns and thanked them all for doing business with them.
This Pyke first appeared in "Infested," the thirteenth episode of Star Wars: The Bad Batch. He was voiced by Liam O'Brien.
